text: Dictyacium is a genus of flies in the family Sciomyzidae. There are at least two described species in Dictyacium. ==Species== *D. ambiguum (Loew, 1864) *D. firmum Steyskal, 1956 ==References== ==Further reading== * * * ==External links== * Category:Acalyptratae Category:Sciomyzoidea genera
